QuestData.Title: Meet with Hretar Riverspeaker
QuestData.Description: An urgent message just arrived for you, $n. It's from Hretar Riverspeaker, one of the shaman trainers in Orgrimmar. He requests your presence as soon as possible.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Hretar Riverspeaker at The Barracks in Orgrimmar.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Hretar Riverspeaker at The Barracks in Orgrimmar.
